OL,3,CUK's longest indoor snow centre and
OL,4,Chuge hotel approved for Welsh town
OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil is going to be home to
OL,7,Fthe UK's longest indoor snow centre
OL,8,Fafter plans were given the green light.
OL,10,FMajor plans for the new indoor ski
OL,11,Fslope and leisure resort in Merthyr
OL,12,FTydfil have been approved by
OL,13,Fcouncillors after Welsh Government
OL,14,Fdecided not to call them in and so now
OL,15,Fthe Rhydycar West development can go
OL,16,Fahead.
