OL,3,CUK's longest indoor snow centre and
OL,4,Chuge hotel approved for Welsh town
OL,6,FThe development on land to the south
OL,7,Fwest of the A470/A4102 roundabout
OL,8,Fincludes an indoor ski slope, water
OL,9,Fpark, indoor activity centre, outdoor
OL,10,Factivity centre, up to 418 bedrooms of
OL,11,Fhotel accommodation, up to 30 units of
OL,12,Fwoodland lodge accommodation and up to
OL,13,F830 car parking spaces.
OL,15,FIt is set to be the official training
OL,16,Fheadquarters for the GB and Welsh
OL,17,Fnational, Olympic and Paralympic snow
OL,18,Fsports teams.
