OL,3,CUK's longest indoor snow centre and
OL,4,Chuge hotel approved for Welsh town
OL,6,FAnd it is now set to become a reality
OL,7,Fafter Merthyr Tydfil Council's
OL,8,Fplanning committee approved it on
OL,9,FWednesday, January 7.
OL,11,FCouncillor Andrew Barry said their
OL,12,Ffirst priority is to look after the
OL,13,Fpeople of the area.
OL,15,FHe said that to pull Merthyr out of
OL,16,Fdeprivation "we need positive economic
OL,17,Fsolutions."
OL,19,FHe said they are going to have growth
OL,20,Fthrough applications of the magnitude
OL,21,Fthat they were taking about here.
