OL,6,FCllr Barry said it gives them the
OL,7,Fopportunity to create small businesses
OL,8,Fand give people aspiration and he
OL,9,Fmentioned the supply chain for the
OL,10,Fdevelopment as well as growth in the
OL,11,Flocal economy and the wider region.
OL,13,FHe said: "We have the opportunity to
OL,14,Fchange the whole socio economic
OL,15,Fdynamic of Merthyr here."
