OL,6,FCouncillor Brent Carter said this
OL,7,Fproject is "ground breaking" and a
OL,8,F"complete game changer for Merthyr
OL,9,FTydfil."
OL,11,FHe said the amount of support for it
OL,12,Fis overwhelming and that he is
OL,13,F"thrilled" about the project.
OL,15,FHe said it would "massively support
OL,16,Fand boost our economy in Merthyr
OL,17,FTydfil" and said it was an ideal
OL,18,Fopportunity to confirm Merthyr Tydfil
OL,19,Fas a "world class destination of
OL,20,Fchoice.
