OL,6,FWelsh Government had previously
OL,7,Fdirected the council not to grant
OL,8,Fplanning permission for the
OL,9,Fapplication in order to allow for
OL,10,Ffurther consideration as to whether or
OL,11,Fnot the application should be referred
OL,12,Fto the Welsh ministers for their
OL,13,Fdetermination.
OL,15,FIn March 2025, the planning committee
OL,16,Fvoted not to support officer
OL,17,Frecommendations to refuse the
OL,18,Fapplication.
