OL,6,FAnd in November 2025, the council
OL,7,Freceived confirmation from Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment that the application would
OL,9,Fnot be called in by Welsh ministers.
OL,11,FThe cabinet secretary for economy,
OL,12,Fenergy and planning concluded that
OL,13,Fwhile issues of conflict with national
OL,14,Fpolicy exist, in this case they are of
OL,15,Fa scale and
OL,17,Fcomplexity which she is content for
OL,18,Fthe local planning authority to
OL,19,Fconsider.
