OL,6,FThe report for committee on January 7
OL,7,Fsays that Welsh Government have
OL,8,Facknowledged that issues of conflict
OL,9,Fwith national planning policy exist
OL,10,Fand the original recommendation to
OL,11,Fcommittee is maintained.
OL,13,FBut it added that given that members
OL,14,Fhave resolved to not accept the
OL,15,Fofficer recommendation, it was before
OL,16,Fmembers to approve the application
OL,17,Fsubject to conditions and heads of
OL,18,Fterms for a section 106 agreement.
